headline: Sapphire ads were ‘puffery,’ BBB says
summary: When JPMorgan Chase advertised its Chase Sapphire Reserve cards as the “most rewarding,” the bank card issuer should have provided more context, the BBB’s National Programs’ advertising arm determined in response to a challenge brought by Capital One.
